        "description": {
            "value": "<p>When wielded in battle, these silver lances blaze with light. A <em>radiant lance</em> is a <em>+2 greater striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Holy] @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Flaming] silver lance</em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>When wielded in battle, the <em>radiant lance</em> sheds bright light in a 60-foot radius.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>On a hit against an undead creature that is specifically vulnerable to sunlight, the lance bursts with a brilliant flash of light, and that undead must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:35] save. If the attack was a critical hit, the undead uses an outcome one degree of success worse than the result of its saving throw.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The undead is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The undead is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The undead is slowed 1 for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> command, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You point the lance at a foe and call out, firing a beam with the effects of a 7th-rank @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Holy Light].</p>"
